						<div class="postbody">Well, I'm hoping to be done with the questions in about 3 &amp; 1/2 to 4 months, and with this format for the game, I'm now planning on having a lot more questions than I did originally. The range will now be from 3,000-3,500 questions so there will be a lot of variety and it won't repeat for a while.
