<br />
<br />New info regarding the game: 
<br />* I've narrowed the name of the game down to two choices: "The Trivia Link" &amp; "Trivia Connected" (the front-runner to me). 
<br />* With each trivia chain, I'd like each question to be presented in this way: Questions &amp; the four multiple choices in a box. Starting with question 1, there will be a line on the right side of the box going off the screen. If it is answered correctly, the screen will pan to the next question. So the gimmick is that whether you're playing the 10, 20, or 30 question link, all the questions will be visually connected (with only one question displayed on the screen at a time), with the final one connected to nothing at the right.</div>

